        <!-- Header Section -->
        <header>
            <h1>Dr. A.P.J. Abdul Kalam</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Missile Man of India & Former President</p>
        </header>

        <!-- About Section -->
        <section id="about" class="card">
            <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/b/b0/A._P._J._Abdul_Kalam.jpg" alt="Dr. A.P.J. Abdul Kalam">
            <p>
                Avul Pakir Jainulabdeen Abdul Kalam (1931–2015) was an Indian aerospace scientist and the 11th President of India. 
                Known as the "Missile Man of India" for his work on ballistic missile and launch vehicle technology, 
                he inspired millions through his vision for a developed India.
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Achievements Section -->
        <section id="achievements" class="card">
            <h2>Major Achievements</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Played a pivotal role in India's Pokhran-II nuclear tests in 1998.</li>
                <li>Developed India's first indigenous Satellite Launch Vehicle (SLV-III).</li>
                <li>Authored inspirational books like *Wings of Fire* and *Ignited Minds*.</li>
                <li>Served as the 11th President of India (2002–2007).</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Quotes Section -->
        <section id="quotes" class="card">
            <h2>Inspirational Quote</h2>
            <blockquote>
                "Dream, dream, dream. Dreams transform into thoughts and thoughts result in action."
            </blockquote>
        </section>
